{"lemma":"خِطامِ","slug":"خِطامِ","root":"خ.ط.م","root_slug":"خ-ط-م","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ط-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11045"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%90%D8%B7%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a cord or rope attached to the nose or jaws of a camel, noseband"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/xi.tˤaːm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11045","headword_ar":"خِطَامٌ","root":"xTm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of halter for a camel; a cord of which one end is fastened round the nose and jaws of a camel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to J,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimaAmN","text_ar":"زِمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but the following explanations are more correct:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain thing well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so called because ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it lies upon"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surrounds"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fore part of the nose and the nouth of the camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything that is put upon the nose of the camel in order that he may be led thereby:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rope, which is put upon the neck of the camel, and folded"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yusam~aY","text_ar":"يُسَمَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", in my copy of the work from which this is taken, I read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuvonaY","text_ar":"يُثْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in another explanation, below,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over, his nose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rope, which is attached to an iron that surrounds the nose and jaws"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (JK:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any cord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rope, that is suspended upon the throat of the camel and then tied upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over, his nose, whether of skin or of wool or of fibres of the palm-tree or of hemp:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, TA:) but if of plaited leather, it is said to be called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jariyrN","text_ar":"جَرِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTAm","text_ar":"خطام"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the camel is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rope, of fibres of the palm-tree, or of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats'"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of flax, at one end of which is put a ring, then the other end is tied to it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. to the rope, as the relative pronoun in the original shows, or to some part of it,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it becomes like a ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loop"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"then it is put upon the neck of the camel, and then it is folded upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over, his nose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"what is put in the nose, [attached to a ring, or the like, therein,] and is slender, is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimaAmN","text_ar":"زِمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAth, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTumN","text_ar":"خُطُمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaEa xiTaAmahu","text_ar":"مَنَعَ خِطَامَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a camel, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He refused to have his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTAm","text_ar":"خطام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put upon him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazaw~aja EalaY xiTaAmK","text_ar":"تَزَوَّجَ عَلَى خِطَامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He married two wives, so that they became like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTaAm","text_ar":"خِطَام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A brand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mark made with a hot iron, upon the nose of a camel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaTomN","text_ar":"خَطْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":":"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTAm","text_ar":"خطام"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spreads upon the camel's two cheeks:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says Aboo-'Alee, in the “ Tedhkireh: ” (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a mark upon the side"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroD","text_ar":"عُرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaroD","text_ar":"عَرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his face, extending to the cheek,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(En-Nadr, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the form of a line:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(En-Nadr, TA:) sometimes the camel is branded with one such mark, and sometimes with two; and one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamalN","text_ar":"جَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTaAmK","text_ar":"خِطَامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoTuwmu","text_ar":"مَخْطُومُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTaAmayoni","text_ar":"خِطَامَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", making"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mxTwm","text_ar":"مخطوم"},{"kind":"text","text":"to govern the gen. case as a prefixed noun; (En-Nadr, K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi xiTaAmN","text_ar":"بِهِ خِطَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTaAmaAn","text_ar":"خِطَامَان"},{"kind":"text","text":". (En-Nadr, TA.) ―         -b3-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rope"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a bucket. (TA.) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspensory"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a bow. (AHn, K, TA.) And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"string"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a bow. (K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","M","K","Mgh","JK","ISh","TA","IAth"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}